des:
Job Complaints is a judgement free zone to complain about your job. 

After sharing your complaints, Alexa will walk you through a few reflection questions to help get you thinking about your next steps.

Built by Nicolle Merrill, author of the new career book, Punch Doubt in the Face: How to Upskill, Change Careers, and Beat the Robots
